<topic id="json-outline-view">
  <title>JSON Outline View</title>
  <prolog>
    <metadata>
      <keywords>
        <indexterm>JSON documents<indexterm>Outline view</indexterm></indexterm>
      </keywords>
    </metadata>
  </prolog>
  <body>
    <p>The <uicontrol>Outline</uicontrol> view for JSON documents displays the list of all the
      components of the JSON document you are editing. By default, it is displayed on the left side
      of the editor. <ph conkeyref="reusables-user-guide/reopen-view"/></p>
    <p product="developer editor">
      <fig>
        <title>JSON Outline View</title>
        <image href="../img/sa_json_outline_view.png"/>
      </fig>
    </p>
    <p product="developerEclipse editorEclipse">
      <fig>
        <title>JSON Outline View</title>
        <image href="../img/ec_json_outline_view.png"/>
      </fig>
    </p>
    <p>The following actions are available in the contextual menu of the JSON
        <uicontrol>Outline</uicontrol> view:<ul>
        <li><uicontrol><image href="../img/Cut16.png" id="image_jmb_pz1_5r"/> Cut</uicontrol></li>
        <li><uicontrol><image href="../img/Copy16.png" id="image_s1v_2st_tr"/> Copy</uicontrol></li>
        <li><uicontrol><image href="../img/Paste16.png" id="image_ms5_gqt_tr"/>
          Paste</uicontrol></li>
        <li><uicontrol><image href="../img/Remove16.png" id="image_mb5_xt4_5r"/>
          Delete</uicontrol></li>
      </ul></p>
    <p>The <ph product="editor developer"><uicontrol><image href="../img/Settings16.png"
            id="image_hgq_dhg_ks"/> Settings</uicontrol> menu on the JSON
          <uicontrol>Outline</uicontrol> view toolbar</ph><ph
        product="editorEclipse developerEclipse"><uicontrol>View menu</uicontrol> on the JSON
          <uicontrol>Outline</uicontrol> view action bar</ph> includes a <uicontrol><image
          href="../img/CaretUpdateOff16.png" id="image_gnv_qft_tr"/> Selection update on cursor
        move</uicontrol> option that allows you to control the synchronization between the
        <uicontrol>Outline</uicontrol> view and source the document. <ph keyref="product"/>
      synchronizes the selection in the <uicontrol>Outline</uicontrol> view with the cursor moves or
      the changes you make in the JSON editor. Selecting one of the components from the
        <uicontrol>Outline</uicontrol> view also selects the corresponding item in the source
      document.</p>
  </body>
